cience History Association|location=Atlanta, GA|author-link=Ligon Duncan|df=mdy-all}} * {{Citation | last = Durand | first = Greg Loren | year = 2014 | title = Judicial Warfare: Christian Reconstruction and Its Blueprints For Dominion | place = Toccoa, GA | publisher = Sola Fide Publishers | edition = third | url = https://www.amazon.com/Judicial-Warfare-Christian-Reconstruction-Blueprints/dp/0692240608}} * {{cite book|last1=McVicar|first1=Michael J.|title=Christian Reconstruction: R. J. Rushdoony and American Religious Conservatism|date=2015|publisher=University of North Carolina Press|location=Chapel Hill|isbn=1469622742}} *{{cite episode|last=Moyers|first=Bill (producer)|author-link=Bill Moyers|title=On Earth as It Is in Heaven|series=God and Politics|number=3|network=Acorn Media|date=January 1, 1987|asin=B006RLPCC2}} *{{citation|last=Smith|first=Chris|title=His Truth is Marching On|magazine=California|date=Fall 2012|url=http://alumni.berkeley.edu/news/california-magazine/fall-2012-politics-issue/his-truth-marching|accessdate=August 23, 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130415082218/http://alumni.berkeley.edu/news/california-magazine/fall-2012-politics-issue/his-truth-marching|archivedate=April 15, 2013|deadurl=no}} * {{Citation |last=Sugg|first=John|title=A Nation Under God|magazine=[[Mother Jones (magazine)|Mother Jones]]|date=December 2005|url = https://www.motherjones.com/news/feature/2005/12/a_nation_under_god.html |accessdate=August 23, 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622235015/https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2005/12/nation-under-god|archivedate=June 22, 2013|deadurl=no}}
