* [[The Executioner (1963 film)|''El verdugo'']] (1963) was voted the best Spanish film of all time with 77 votes in a 1995 poll of 100 critics and film professionals organized by Spanish film magazine ''{{ill|lt=Nickel Odeon|Nickel Odeon (magazine)|es|Nickel Odeon (revista)}}''.<ref>{{cite magazine|date=Winter 1995|title=Cien españoles y el cine español|magazine=Nickel Odeon|issue=1|url=http://www.nickel-odeon.com/numeros/a01.htm}}</ref>

